Second beta of de westwood pro.
===============================

-------------------------------

Important things to know: 
=========================

1.The doors from the orginal where you get stuck are fixed. 

2.The fog is gone.

3.Some areas were changed a little, but it is nearly the same westwood you know.

-----------------------------------------

Differences to first beta:
==========================

1.This version is with all the westwood sounds you know.

2.And this version has an overview and radar.

-------------------------------------------------
Addon in this download which you dont have to use:
==================================================

1.Animated spray (.vtf) which adverts this map ;-)

---------------------------------------------------

Wanna test without installing?
============================

**134.255.219.180:25113**
